conda branch
============

This branch is the merge of logging-fixes + sh-replacement branches + changes to make it to work in conda.

TL;DR;

conda create -n kivy autoconf automake setuptools pkg-config cython openstep-parser pbxproj
conda activate kivy

python toolchain.py build --arch arm64 libffi -v
python toolchain.py build --arch arm64 openssl -v
python toolchain.py build --arch arm64 python3 -v
